text: Monique Wismeijer (born 21 October 1978 in Amsterdam) is a Dutch volleyball player. She played at the 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship and 2009 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for TVC Amstelveen. == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
